# ragdoll-cat is tracked here (demo repo), but block sensitive files.
# Most secrets (*.jks, *.keystore, keystore.properties, local.properties,
# google-services.json, *.env-style) are already covered by ragdoll-cat/.gitignore.
# These symlinks point to personal credential paths outside the repo — never commit them.
ragdoll-cat/.env
ragdoll-cat/.mcp.json
# Debug keystore (ragdoll-cat/.gitignore only covers cs_release.keystore + *.jks)
ragdoll-cat/*.keystore
# Note: cs_release.keystore.gpg is GPG-encrypted and intentionally kept (safe to commit).
